Copy the script into your machine and grant execute permission to execute this.
chmod  774 /home/chinu/perform_task.ksh
Run with complete path as
$/home/chinu/perform_task.ksh

It ask for the inputs  for the operations. Please follows the instructions asked by the script.
For password change need to login as root user.
For remote machine login or remote execution, The script ask for  password  to enter interactively.It can be remediate by  secure key sharing between the servers
